---
// src/layouts/TelegramLayout.astro
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
  <header class="mb-4 rounded-3xl border border-base-content/8 bg-base-100/55 px-5 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm md:px-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-primary/75">
      <i class="ri-sparkling-line"></i>
      <span>Recent Updates</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-base-content/92">
      最近动态
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base-content/62 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
      一些简短记录、过程切片和暂时还不打算写成长文的想法。
    </p>
  </header>

  <div id="dynamic-feed-container" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <slot />
  </div>
</section>
